FT  16 AUG 94 / UK Company News: Portmeirion ahead 18% to Pounds 1.88m
Portmeirion Potteries (Holdings) reported profits of Pounds 1.88m pre-tax
for the six months to June 30 - an 18 per cent rise on the comparable Pounds
1.59m.
Turnover from continuing operations expanded some 12 per cent to Pounds
12.7m (Pounds 11.4m).
The interim dividend goes up from 2.25p to 2.5p, payable from earnings of
11.85p (9.88p) per share.
